description:
\[episode conversation section\]
 
SG: NONONO~\!Senpai\!\!GIVE IT BACK\!\!THAT’S NOT FUNNY\!\! 
TS: come and get it yourself~~you silly little sister~~or i’ll tell the whole school how adorable you are~\! :3
 
\==
 
Hello,every pony,and i’m back. 
with my new artwork. 
This one i was going to post it on Friday but i got another artwork need to be done at first, so i chosing on today.
 
it’s the satellite for this artwork 
\>\>1444541s
 
if you do recall , i said that this “Sweet as a cake,smooth as a minuet” was drewing in commission’s specification 
so that means i will also drew the “bonus artwork” for this. (it’s the artwork if your commission charge over than 40 dollars and you will get it, it’s very usually present it as one of the series of “AcademyLIVE season”)
 
i guess you guys remember one of thi series’s episode “My roommate senpai”
 
\>\>1272621s
 
and this one is the reprise episode. once again , Starlight Glimmer having a very hard living with her roommate and her senpai─Princess TwilightSparkle, and this sence is when TS found SG’s “secret little diary” ,which having a lot of silly drewing by Starlight about how she admired her “senpai”and Starlight find out that was so embarrasssing and trying to grab the book back, but her senpai actually find out this is so much fun “playing” with her……… 
but they both like each other with their very own heart…
 
WHAT? you ask me do i ship them? 
well, kind of yes, but not big fan of it(what i’m really shipping very hard in this academyLIVE series is TrixieXMaudie \<3 ) 
but i was thinking the relationship between them both are very lovely somehow. and that’s what inspiring me to drew this.
 
oh, by the way. 
another reason i drew this is that because i’m also finished another music piece of “The diamond musicbox” and this artwork will be present as the cover of the new music work , well. on different background actually. 
so wait for my message, and hope you will enjoy my music work too.
 
 
please leave the comment and share it to someone else if you like,thank you for your supporting
 
Sean.M
